descriptionHtml:
\"The Enchiridion (which translates to \"The Handbook\" or \"The Manual\") was an ancient book with codes of conduct, guidelines, and other helpful information for heroes. The book had great power which allowed it to tear open worm holes between dimensions in the multiverse\"
                                                                                                          - Adventure Time wiki 

The archive contains mesh and textures for modders. You can add this as static or working book (if you write it) to your plugins.

Esp is not included.
author: Horinf
